pageContext.claim: “[Past administrations] imposed radical restrictions on our farmers and ethanol producers...We took [E15] all year long, not the very shortened year. And nobody could explain to me why. Not one person was able to explain why they cut it off.”
pageContext.analysis: It’s highly doubtful that “nobody could explain” the reasoning behind the Obama-era restrictions. A simple Google search would show they were imposed in 2011 to reduce smog pollution.
